description:
An update to the 4chan navframe for those who can't live without it. (me)
Designed to match with: http://userstyles.org/styles/10323

/* 11/21/08 : Version 1
/* 11/22/08 : Updated to account for change in nav frame address.
/* 11/23/08 : Christ, make up your mind what and where the nav file is already.

css:
@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);

@-moz-document url-prefix("http://www.4chan.org/frames") {

#logo 
  { background-image: url("http://img508.imageshack.us/img508/3475/minileafgreenqp2.png") !important; }

body 
  { margin-left: 10% !important;
    margin-right: 10% !important;
    background-color: #ffffff !important;
    background-image: url("http://img211.imageshack.us/img211/2628/fadegreenbe8.png") !important;
    color: #000 !important;
    font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;
    font-size: 11px !important; }

a 
  { color: #669933 !important; 
    font-weight: 700 !important; }

a:hover
  { font-weight: 200 !important;
    font-size: 12px !important; 
    font-weight: 700 !important; }

h2
  { color: #ffffff !important;
    background: #669933 !important;
    -moz-border-radius: 1em !important;
    border: 1px solid #336600 !important;
    padding: 5px !important;
    font-size: 12px !important;
    opacity: 0.5 !important; }

h2:hover
  { color: #ffffff !important;
    background: #669933 !important;
    -moz-border-radius: 1em !important;
    border: 1px solid #336600 !important;
    padding: 5px !important;
    font-size: 12px !important;
    opacity: 1.0 !important; }

.plus
  { background: #669933 !important;
    -moz-border-radius: 1em !important;
    border: 1px solid #336600 !important;
    opacity: 0.5 !important; }

.plus:hover
  { background: #669933 !important;
    -moz-border-radius: 1em !important;
    border: 1px solid #336600 !important;
    opacity: 1.0 !important; }

}
